		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/切玛利的遮荫.assets/Image_14.png')" x="719" y="714">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/切玛利的遮荫.assets/Image_15.png')" x="1391" y="713">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「遮荫」在前方召唤出2枚<span textDecoration="underline">水泡</span><span>，水泡缓慢追踪玩家并崩破，每个水泡造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span><span color="#bfffff">水泡可冻结，可击回破盾。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="438" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「遮荫」在玩家处召唤<span textDecoration="underline">流泉</span><span>，造成一次</span><span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span><span color="#bfffff">流泉可冻结，可抵挡「败众淮渊」的伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="511" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「遮荫」朝玩家方向蓄力，迸发水元素冲流，造成<span color="#7fbfff">70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="799" width="441" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「遮荫」召出6股流泉，各造成<span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害；接着进行长达10s的喷流，持续造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">250%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="799" width="426" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「遮荫」进行蓄力，重新形成<span textDecoration="underline">流泉之灵界</span><span>；场地边缘开始出现缓慢朝其移动的水泡，尝试接触会造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">50%</span><span>伤害；接着进行长达30s的蓄力过程。蓄力完成后，将进行一次涌海裂罚，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">400%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="912" width="430" height="116" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">水泡：可被冰冻结，冻结后可被重击击回，命中护盾则-<span color="#7fbfff">64水</span><span>并造成</span><span color="#99ffff">440%</span><span>基础倍率的伤害；若在技能「噬众苦泉」期间被「遮荫」吸收，则护盾+</span><span color="#7fbfff">64水</span><span>。<br/>流泉：可被冰冻结，冻结后可抵挡「败众淮渊」的伤害，<br/>流泉之灵界：</span><span color="#7fbfff">320水</span><span>盾，开局自带，击破后可瘫痪「遮荫」10s，并使其受到的伤害提升</span><span color="#ffcdbf">100%</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
